<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>404 | Page Not Found</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-color: #fcfcfc;
            --text-main: #1a1a1a;
            --text-secondary: #888;
            --accent: #151019;
        }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            color: var(--text-main);
            margin: 0;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            height: 100vh;
            text-align: center;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 20px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: clamp(80px, 15vw, 120px);
            font-weight: 800;
            margin: 0;
            letter-spacing: -0.05em;
            
            /* 1. Fallback color for older browsers */
            color: var(--accent); 
            
            /* 2. The Gradient */
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--accent) 0%, #444 100%);
            
            /* 3. Clipping logic */
            background-clip: text;
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            
            /* 4. Make original text transparent so gradient shows through */
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            
            line-height: 1;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            max-width: 400px;
            margin: 10px auto 30px auto;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 14px 28px;
            background-color: var(--accent);
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 15px;
            transition: transform 0.2s, filter 0.2s;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            filter: brightness(1.2);
        }

        /* Subtle background element */
        .decoration {
            position: absolute;
            font-size: 20vw;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: rgba(0,0,0,0.02);
            z-index: -1;
            user-select: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="decoration">?</div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <h1>404</h1>
        <p>This page has either moved or never existed in the first place.</p>
        <a href="/" class="btn">Return Home</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>